==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Starlike
<hw>Star"like`</hw> <pr>(-l⟦imac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Resembling a star; stellated; radiated like a star; <as>as,
<ex>starlike</ex> flowers</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Shining; bright; illustrious.</def>
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The having turned many to righteousness shall confer a
<qex>starlike</qex> and immortal brightness.</q>
<rj><qau>Boyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Starling</ent>⟦br⟧
